_sText:
This is my 5th map, 1st cs:s map...
Port of one of my 1.6 maps...

Well turns out i had backed up the .rmf to my 1.6 map haha... so i took peoples advice of "Jesus Christ u gotta make this for cs:s!!", and made it for it...

I gave it a overhaul so that it can be considered a cs:s map...

I would think the map would play good in a death match server cuz its from a deathmathc game XD

I hope you like and plz comment when if you try it, i didnt make a radar overview for it cuz i dont know how to sry, once i find out ill update this for it....

This is a map that can be found in the video game timesplitters 1-3...

Here is the .txt file, with a story line and all haha...

cs_chinese (v1.0) - Hostage Rescue
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Edited by: HottStepper (ItsV1be@aim.com.com)
Received mapping tips from fpsbanana.com and Counter-Strike.net forums
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Setting: China Town, Night, High 60's, Spring.

Story: A group of terrorist decided to take a break and eat at the best chinese restorant in China Town.  Disatisfied with thier meals, decided to go back to what they do best, and hold some hostages to get thier money back and then some.

Objectives:

Counter-Terrorist: Rescue the hostages, or eliminate the Terrorist.

Terrorist: Defend and protect the hostages, or eliminate the Counter-Terrorist.
